query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('serverfault')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('active-directory',
'apache-2.2',
'apache-2.4',
'exchange',
'ftp',
'iptables',
'nginx',
'permissions',
'virtualization',
'vmware-esxi',
'windows');
